Name: Ancient Medieval Empire
About the game: Ancient Medieval Empire is a strategy game with RPG elements. Owning kingdom lands has never been an easy job. A huge number of free castles and villages, which greatly attract the evil orcs. Manage your army, capture new castles and fight back against enemies. You have to capture as many castles as possible and drive away the orcs. Features: - Random generation of locations. - Nice graphics. - Enemies adaptive to game progress.
